Silly satanic elite, bunkers will NOT save you from the WRATH of the LAMB!!!
The satanic Torahless elite think they can hide from the WRATH of the LAMB, Return of Yeshua Mashiyach of Netzaret, and Yom YeHoVaH!!!
Rev 6:15 And the sovereigns of the earth, and the great ones, and the rich ones, and the commanders, and the mighty, and every slave and every free one, hid themselves in the caves and in the rocks of the mountains,
Rev 6:16 and said to the mountains and rocks, “Fall on us and hide us (Hos_10:8) from the face of Him sitting on the throne and from the wrath of the Lamb,
Rev 6:17 because the great day of His wrath has come, and who is able to stand?”
Below is the word used for "caves", and let me assure you, bunkers and DUMBs fit PERFECTLY!!!
speilaion
spay'-lah-yon
Neuter of a presumed derivation of speos (a grotto); a cavern; by implication a hiding place or resort: - cave, den.
The ONLY hope for mankind and the earth is Yom YeHoVaH and Return of the ORIGINAL Torah Mashiyach Yeshua of Netzaret!!!
Baruch Haba B'Shem YeHoVaH!!!
Make sure you are found in Yeshua Mashiyach of Netzaret, it is called THE GOOD NEWS for a reason!!!
Eliyah
